* Store passwords securely using bcrypt or Argon2.
* Use JWT for API authentication.
* Apply role-based access control using `user_school_roles` and optionally `roles_permissions`.
* Restrict direct database access to trusted application services.
* Enable backup and point-in-time recovery for production databases.
* Encrypt sensitive fields in transit and at rest where required.

